# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# MenYou .gitignore
# Based on the GitHub VisualStudio.gitignore template + project-specific
# entries for Avalonia, installer artifacts, and Windows tooling.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Build output --------------------------------------------------------
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Dd]ebug[Pp]ublic/
[Rr]elease/
[Rr]eleases/
x64/
x86/
ARM64/
[Ww][Ii][Nn]32/
build/
bld/
out/
publish/
[Aa]rtifacts/

# --- Installer / release artifacts --------------------------------------
# Inno Setup (iscc) drops MenYou-Setup-<ver>.exe under .\dist\; `choco
# pack` can produce a local .nupkg. We commit none of this — the GitHub
# Actions release workflow regenerates everything from source on each tag
# push. Releases/ is an additional installer output dir, also ignored.
dist/
Releases/
*.nupkg
*.snupkg

# --- .NET tooling --------------------------------------------------------
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/
*.csproj.user
*.vbproj.user
*.binlog
*.svclog
*.scc
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
**/coverage.cobertura.xml
**/TestResults/
.dotnet/

# --- Visual Studio --------------------------------------------------------
.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.userprefs
*.psess
*.vsp
*.vspx
*.sap
*.tlog
*.opendb
*.VC.db
*.VC.VC.opendb
*.dbmdl
*.dbproj.schemaview
*.jfm
.ntvs_analysis.dat
node_modules/

# --- Rider / ReSharper ---------------------------------------------------
.idea/
*.sln.iml
_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper
*.DotSettings.user

# --- VS Code -------------------------------------------------------------
.vscode/

# --- Native (MenYou.Bridge) ----------------------------------------------
# The C++/VC project drops its intermediates under bin/obj already (caught
# above) but Visual Studio occasionally emits these in-tree.
*.iobj
*.ipdb
*.aps
*.ncb
*.opensdf
*.sdf
*.sln.cache
ipch/
dlldata.c

# --- Avalonia ------------------------------------------------------------
# Avalonia's compiled-bindings + XAML-loader generators land in obj/, which
# is already ignored. Nothing extra needed.

# --- Logs / temp ---------------------------------------------------------
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
*.swp
*~
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
.DS_Store

# --- Local-only secrets --------------------------------------------------
*.local.json
*.local.config
secrets.json
appsettings.Local.json
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- SignPath / signing local-only artifacts -----------------------------
# In case someone runs `signtool` locally against a personal cert.
*.pfx
*.p12
*.snk
!signing/example.snk

# --- Inno Setup / WiX local builds (if added later) ---------------------
*.iss.user

# --- Local research / scratch (not part of the shipped project) ---------
# Vendored Open-Shell source kept locally for reference; never committed.
openshell_research/

# --- Claude / agent metadata --------------------------------------------
.claude/
